<plot>Young Jaime (Libby Letlow) wants nothing more than her mother's love and approval. But when her efforts interfere with a romantic affair, her mother, Dana (Kelly Galindo) invents frightening bedtime stories to control her. These scare tactics keep Jaime in line and seem harmless...until Jaime starts to believe that the scary stories are actually happening to her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?542654</url></doc>
